channel.title: Error_game_invalidhost.ws
channel.description:
I'm trying to get a 562 webclient working, and when i upload the .jar file and go to the html for it www.retributionx.org/webclient it then takes me to www.retributionx.org/webclient/error_game_invalidhost.ws
Not a clue what's going on please help

item.title: Error_game_invalidhost.ws
item.dc:creator: @Samih1996 Samih1996
item.description:
@Samih1996 wrote:

Davidi2:

The IP it’s trying to connect to isn’t valid. This means the client source you’re using either forgot to remove the check or is using the wrong IP.

hi there david, can you be more specific? I have the same problem. My server is online and the ip is set to the correct computer so it should be playable. what did you mean either “you forgot to remove the check”?

Thanks.
